        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You kick up a wind at a point you can see, creating a small, continuous 5ft diameter twister.&nbsp; <br /> Any creature that starts its turn within 5ft of the twister must make a Strength (Save) check or be lifted 10ft into the air and shoved 10ft away from the twister.&nbsp; If the creature is inside the twister, they take this save at disadvantage and are thrown 20ft upward upon failure instead.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>In addition, the winds of the twister disrupt ranged attacks shot within 5ft of it, reducing the chance to hit by -2.&nbsp; <br /> You can move the twister up to 10ft each turn as a minor action.</p>",
